  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "To address these issues, a growing number of researchers are investigating the use of LLMs themselves as intermediaries for carrying out these subjective assessments.",
    "For example, in ChemCrow [75], researchers assess the experimental results using GPT.",
    "They consider both the completion of tasks and the accuracy of the underlying processes.",
    "Similarly, ChatEval [161] introduces a novel approach by employing multiple agents to critique and assess the results generated by various candidate models in a structured debate format.",
    "This innovative use of LLMs for evaluation purposes holds promise for enhancing both the credibility and applicability of subjective assessments in the future."
  ],
